SPACE 2014 class project

If downloaded from github it must be placed under a directory named PycharmProjects.
The directory PycharmProjects must be located under the users home directory.  The
$HOME environment variable is used by this program to load elements before creating
the scenes generated by this program.

An example of a path used:

$HOME/PycharmProjects/space2014/graphics/SpaceStation/scenes/sun.ma

Also, its important that Maya have a new or empty scene before attempting to run
any of the programs associated with this project.  Maya errors will be generated
if the scene is not new or empty.
